<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV4">
<l>taṉineñca muṉṉavar puḷḷē kavarntatu taṇṇantuḻāyk</l>
<l>kiṉineñca miṅkuk kavarvati yāmilam nīnaṭuvē</l>
<l>muṉivañca pēycci mulaicuvait tāṉmuṭi cūṭutuḻāyp</l>
<l>paṉinañca māruta mēyemma tāvi paṉippiyalvē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] lonely heart has been seized by his bird before. Now</l>
<l>we are without a heart to be seized here by the cool tulsi. Meanwhile, you,</l>
<l>wind with the dewy poison of the tulsi worn in the crown of him who tasted</l>
<l>the breast of the hateful treacherous demoness, is it [your] nature to make our soul shiver?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
